  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Right now, when one is logged-in, the nudges on one's own profile page have pink
text, and the arrows are Unicode -&gt; arrows, not &amp;laquo; like we use elsewhere.

Karen thinks we should change the color of the pink links, and make other
changes that she should clarify here. (aldeka, please speak up on this bug.)

(This bug is about the redesign of the site that is occurring during 0.12.02.
You can see that redesign in process, temporarily, here:
<a href="http://gentle-robot-6466.herokuapp.com/">http://gentle-robot-6466.herokuapp.com/</a> )</pre>
